sections.heading: to 61-28-34 - Repealed.
sections.text: Repeals.— Laws 1992, ch. 10, § 30 repealed 61-28-1 to 61-28-34, as enacted by Laws 1947, ch. 115, § 20; Laws 1963, ch. 43, § 27; and as amended by Laws 1983, ch. 15, §§ 5, 7, 10; Laws 1987, ch. 236, §§ 1-29; Laws 1987, ch. 333, § 11; and Laws 1988, ch. 23, § 1, relating to public accountants, effective May 20, 1992. For present comparable provisions,see61-28B-1 NMSA 1978 et seq.
